l:mi>p</mml:mi></mml:mtd></mml:mtr></mml:mtable></mml:mrow></mml:mfenced></mml:math><graphic xlink:href="41467_2022_35328_Article_Equ14.gif" position="anchor"/></alternatives></disp-formula>The moments of <bold>T</bold> can be expressed by <italic>I</italic>, <italic>Λ</italic> and <italic>p</italic>,<disp-formula id="Equ15"><label>10</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M153">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
